Loch Jehoram, ruodh Juda

(
2   Ruodhi 
8  .
16  -
24  )


1  Jehoshafat notho moyike but kwerene e dala Daudi, mi Jehoram wuode nodoko ruoth kare. 
2  Ne en kod owetene ma nyingegi Azaria, Jahiel, Zekaria, Azaria, Mikael, kod Shefatia. Giduto ne gin yawuot Jehoshafat ruodh Juda. 
3  Wuon-gi nopogonigi mwandu mang’eny mag fedha gi dhahabu kod gik moko ma tekregi ng’eny kaachiel gi miech Juda mochiel gohinga. To loch nomiyo Jehoram nimar ne en wuode makayo. 
4  Kane Jehoram osebet e kom duong’ mar wuon mare kendo oguroree, nonego owetene duto kod jodongo moko bende mag Israel.


5  Jehoram ne jahigni piero adek gariyoo kane odoko ruoth, kendo norito piny kuom higni aboro, kodak Jerusalem. 
6  Noluwo timbe ruodhi Israel kaka jodhood Ahab notimo, nimar nokendo jodhood Ahab. Timbene ne richo e nyim Ruoth Nyasaye. 
7  

To kata kamano Ruoth Nyasaye ne ok otieko dhood Daudi, nikech nosesingorene kaachiel gi nyikwaye ni anywolane nobed e kom duong’ ka taya malielne nyaka chieng’.


8  

E ndalo loch Jehoram, jo-Edom nodagi bet e bwo loch Juda, mi ne giketo ruodhgi giwegi. 
9  Omiyo Jehoram nodhi kuno kaachiel gi jodonge mag lweny gi gechene duto, to jo-Edom nolworogi, mi Jehoram gi jotend gechene nochiew gotieno momwomo. 
10  Mano e kaka jo-Edom notieko loch Juda e Edom nyaka chil kawuono. E ndalogo Libna bende nodagi bedo e bwo loch Jehoram, nimar noseweyo Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasach kwerene.


11  Bende noloso hembko mane ni kuonde moting’ore e piny gode mag Juda, momiyo jo-Jerusalem oweyo Ruoth Nyasaye, kendo omiyo jo-Juda oruenyo. 
12  Eka barua noa kuom Elija janabi niya, “Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasach Daudi kwaru owacho kama, 
13  ‘Nakel masira maduong’ kuom jogi gi nyithindgi gi mondi kod gigi duto, 
14  kendo in iwuon nibed gi tuo marach ma nocham dhokchindi kuom ndalo mang’eny nyaka giniwuog oko nikech ne ok iluwo timbe Jehoshafat wuoru kata timbe Asa ruodh Juda, 
15  to niluwo mana timbe ruodhi mag Israel. Bende nimiyo jo-Juda gi jo-Israel oweyo Ruoth Nyasaye kaka dhood Ahab nomiyo jo-Israel oweye, kendo ninego oweteni ma yawuot wuoru mane joma kare moloyi.’ ”


16  Ruoth Nyasaye nomiyo jo-Filistia kod jo-Arabu mokiewo gi jo-Kush obedo wasik Jehoram, 
17  mi ne gimonjo jo-Juda kendo ne gikawo gik moko duto mane giyudo e od ruoth kaachiel gi yawuote gi monde, mak mana Ahazia wuode machogo ema nodong’.


18  Bang’ mago duto Ruoth Nyasaye nomiyo tuo mar dhokchin ma ok nyal chango omako Jehoram. 
19  Tuo nomedore, mi bang’ higni ariyo dhokchinde nowuok oko mi notho gi rem malit. Joge ne ok olosone mach kaka nolosni kwerene. 
20  Ne en jahigni piero adek gariyo kane odoko ruoth, kendo norito piny kuom higni aboro kodak Jerusalem. Notho ma onge ng’ama oywage. Ne giyike e dala Daudi, to ok e liete ruodhi.

